{"tid":380423,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聽抒情歌一定聽日文歌1","createTime":"2017-08-30T06:05:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-30T11:19:59.000Z","uid":140357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"81cc6bd007a4d37c65e2f265db080eca84d6f52f","tid":380423,"uid":140357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T06:05:51.000Z","msg":"第一個歌手當然係藤田麻衣子<br />\n利申:小弟手機最多佢嘅歌。<br />\n<br />\n科普: 藤田麻衣子（1984年1月16日－）為日本愛知縣名古屋市綠區出身的創作歌手。 2006年9月以單曲「戀に落ちて」出道，現在共發行了10張單曲及5張專輯。所有的歌曲均由本人親自作詞作曲，歌曲多為抒情曲或打氣曲。除了為自己創作外，也有為其他藝人提供樂曲。 有很多女性歌迷，演唱會有七成觀眾是女性。<br />\n<br />\n第一首推介: 撈金魚<br />\n特點:以金魚的角度去講愛情<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/X4QGjLgf6qg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FX4QGjLgf6qg&d=hOj2yrHBh8ifRT3WMHuv3KWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=dd08cf95\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/X4QGjLgf6qg</a>"},{"pid":"7bc55133773892a5ac1ba7b38a2d50e2b0b55572","tid":380423,"uid":140357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T06:22:39.000Z","msg":"第\u00002\u0000首:哭泣哭泣<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/paUITDSlkQA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpaUITDSlkQA&d=hOj2yrHBh8ifRT3WMHuv3KWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=33f0fbbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/paUITDSlkQA</a>"},{"pid":"ee981628a10cfff78ca8c27895f03d01191d499e","tid":380423,"uid":140357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T11:19:59.000Z","msg":"第2首:哭泣哭泣<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=paUITDSlkQA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DpaUITDSlkQA&d=hOj2yrHBh8ifRT3WMHuv3KWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=97cfd6e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=paUITDSlkQA</a>"}]}